## Recommended Learning Order (2026)

1. Python + FastAPI
2. Git & Docker
3. Prompt Engineering
4. LLM APIs (OpenAI, Gemini, Claude)
5. Embeddings
6. Vector Databases
7. RAG (Basic → Advanced)
8. Tool Calling & Function Calling
9. MCP (Model Context Protocol)
10. AI Agents (LangGraph, OpenAI Agents SDK, CrewAI)
11. Memory Systems (Mem0, Zep, LangMem)
12. Automation (n8n, Zapier, Pipedream)
13. AI Security & Guardrails
14. Observability (LangSmith, LangFuse, Phoenix)
15. Evaluation (Ragas, DeepEval, Promptfoo)
16. LLMOps & Deployment (MLflow, Docker, Kubernetes, BentoML)
17. Fine-tuning (LoRA/QLoRA) and Multimodal AI

Mastering these topics in order will give you the skills needed to build modern production-grade AI assistants, RAG systems, agentic workflows, and enterprise AI applications.
